\ip God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Jonan Eghaghanim, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir igharazibar eghaghanibar m…®n garir puvat…®. Ak…®nafarir kam, Jona amizir bizibara gun m…®gei. Egha uaghan, Jona amizir arazir maba mong derazir puvat…®. 
\ip God Niniven nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamizir God g…®fozir puvat…®ziba bagh akam akunasa Jona m…®keme. Ez…® Jona aghuagha, faragha God…®n ar…® mangasa. Ez…® God uam a inigha ize, egha dughiar kam…®n Jona Niniven ghugha God…®n akam otivizir akabar gun me m…®gei. Egha a gari, me navibagh iraz…®, a kamagh…®n fo God me gas…®ghasighan kogham, ez…® an navim ikuvigha iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God Jona arazir apangkuvim bagha bar deraghav…®ra an sure gami. 
\ip Judan gumazamizir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, God merara ifonge, egha gumazamizir igharaz darazigh ifongezir puvat…®. Ak…®nafarir kam deraghv…®ra kamagh…®n e m…®k…®masa, God nguazim…®n gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra me gifonge. Ez…® ingangarir God Israelia gan…®ngizir mam, a kamak…®n, me gumazamizir igharazibar aku a bagh izam. 
