\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Aposel 27:18-19; 27:38\x*Ez…® kurim…®n suighava an ingarir gumaziba atiatia aguava, vaghvagha akurvazim bagha uan asebar diava arai.\f + \fr 1:5 \ft Kurim…®n ingarir gumazibar aseba, mati en marvir guaba ko as…®zir nedaziba ko aser av…®rir maba uakan.\f* Egha me kurim m…®gh…®vghighasa, kurim…®n itir bizir maba isa ongarim…®n ada akuri. Dughiar kamnagh…®n, Jona kurim…®n d…®k…®nim giraghu, egha akuava ongani. 
