\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Josua 7:14-16; 1 Samuel 10:20-21; Aposel 1:26\x*Ez…® kurim…®n ingarir gumaziba uariv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa iz…® e arazitam damigh fogham, tinara amiz…®ma os…®mt…®zir kam e bato.‚Äù Egha me foghasa uan nguibam…®n arazir mam gikarara zuima Jonan ziam oto. 
