\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uam akam Jona gan…®ga ghaze,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh, Niniven nguibar bar ekiam…®n mang…®. Akar k…® n…® gan…®dim, n…® a is…® gumazamizir nguibar kam…®n itiba, an gun me m…®k…®m.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Jona Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam baregha, d…®kavigha Niniven zui. Ninive a nguibar bar ekiam. N…® nguibar kam fagh vong…®n otivs…®, aruer 3plan anebigh mangam.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4-5 \xt Matyu 12:41; Luk 11:32\x*Ez…® Jona d…®kavigha nguibar ekiar kam…®n averiam…®n ghuava, aruer vam…®ran darorim gamua, kamagh…®n pamtem…®n gumazamizibar d…®a ghaze, ‚Äú40plan dughiaba g…®vaght…®ma, Ninive bar mogh…®ra ikuvigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Niniven gumazamiziba God…®n akar kam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikia, egha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE dagheba ategham. E bar mogh…®ra, gumazir dapaniba ko gumazir k…®niba uaghara, e azir korotiabar aghuigh, egh uan azirakar kam akaght…®, God fogh suam, e guizbang…®ra navibagh iragha g…®fa.‚Äù Egha me m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ami.  
\v 6 Ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam Niniven atrivim batoz…®, an oregha uan Atrivir dabirabim ataki. Egha a uan atrivim…®n korotiar aghuiba suegha, ada arigha azirakar korotiaba aghui, egha averenim gis…®n aperaghav iti, egha kamagh…®n uab…® God…®n akagha ghaze, a uan navim g…®ra. 
\p  
\v 7 Egha atrivim Niniven gumazamiziba bar me bagha akaba amangi. Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar k…®, uan gumazir dapaniba ko en akam. Ia bar mogh…®ra dagheba atakigh. Ia gumazamiziba, ko, uan bulmakauba ko, sipsipba ko, ia d…®patam ko, daghetam aman bar mark…®.  
\v 8 Ia bar mogh…®ra azirakar korotiabar aghuigh, egh uan bulmakauba ko sipsipba azirakar korotiaba uaghan me gikegh. Egh ia m…®gh…®ghv…®ra God ko m…®k…®m, egh ia amir arazir bar kuraba ko pura uariv sogha ariaghirir arazim, ia bar mogh…®ra da atakigh.  
\v 9 E kamagh…®n damight…®ma, God ti ua uan n…®ghn…®zim giragh, egh uam ataran koght…®, e ovengan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Ua Me Ini 32:14; 1 Atriviba 21:27-29; Jeremaia 18:8; Amos 7:3; 7:6\x*Egha me uan arazir kuraba ataki, ez…® God me amizir arazir kam…®n gani. Egha uan n…®ghn…®zim giragha, bizir kurar a Niniven gumazamizibar amuasa m…®kemezim, an a gamizir puvat…®. 
\c 4  
