\v 1 Jona, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Niniven gumazamizibar apangkuvizir arazir kam…®n osemegha, navim an ikufi.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:6-7; Joel 2:13\x*Egha a kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® nan akam barakigh. K…® t…®ghar nguibam atagh…®raghamin dughiam…®n, k…® fo, arazir n…® amizir kam n…® a damuam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ar…® mangasa, egha ara Tarsis…®n zui. K…® fo, n…® gumazamiziba bar me gifongegha, bar men apangkufi. Egha n…® zuam…®rama atarir pu. Puvat…®. N…®n apangkuvim bar mogh…®ram en ekefe. Egha n…® zurara uan n…®ghn…®zim g…®ghasa ifongeghav…®ra ikia, egha gumazamizibar arazir kuraba ikarvazir puvat…®.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt 1 Atriviba 19:4\x*Aria, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® ik…®r…®m…®rir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n itim ag…®fagh. K…® oveght…®, kamagh…®n deragham. K…® oveghan koght…®, kamagh…®n ti deraghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God an akam kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúJona, adarir arazir n…® amir kam a deras, o? Bar puvat…®!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Jona nguibar ekiam ategha ghua aruem anadi nagh…®n apera. Egha a purirpenir mam…®n ingarigha an aven aperaghav iti. Egh an an ik…® nguibar ekiam…®n ganasa, bizir tizimram a bativam.  
\v 6 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgavim, kamagh…®n Jona g…®n…®ghn…®si, aruem an m…®karzim dapongan koght…®ma a derav…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n, a ruarim…®n ikar…®zir mam gamiz…®ma an aghua, Jonan purirpenim…®n ava Jona avara. Ez…® Jona ikar…®zir kam bagha bar akonge.  
\v 7 Ez…® am…®nim tiraz…® am…®mzaraghan m…®zaraghara, God apizir kurar mam amadaz…®ma, a ikar…®zir kam bagha izegha anemez…®, ikar…®zim m…®s…®ngi.  
\v 8 Ez…® g…®n aruem anadima, God am…®nir bar puv…®ra feim amadaz…®ma, an aruem anadi nagh…®n izi. Ez…® aruem Jonan dapanim gaboi, an damaziba an s…®rima a irasava ami. 
\p Ez…® Jona kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha God m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® aremeka. K…® aremeght…®, kamagh…®n deragham. K…® aremeghan koght…®, kamagh…®n deraghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® God kamagh…®n Jona m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkar…®zir kam m…®sigha g…®vaz…®ma, n…® atari. N…®n adarim ti arazir aghuim, o? Bar puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Jona bar God basemegha ghaze, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, nan adarim arazir aghuim. Nan adarim bar ekefe, a na damight…®, k…® aremeght…® deragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Ekiam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkar…®zir kam d…®magarir vam…®ran aghuava ekefe, egha d…®magarir igharazim…®n a m…®s…®ngi. N…® tong an ingarizir puvat…®, egha n…® a gamiz…® an ekevezir puvat…®. Egha bar bizir muziarir kam, n…® an apangkufi.  
\v 11 K…® uaghan apangkuvir ekiam Niniven nguibar bar ekiam…®n iti. An aven, arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®zir borir av…®riba iti, men d…®bobonim 120 tausen gafira. Egha uaghan bulmakaun bar av…®riba iti.‚Äù